data.description: Presenting 15240 Garfield. On and off the market due to no fault of the sellers or the home itself. Two buyers have lost their finances during the transaction, this allows you an opportunity to make this house yours! The seller has made significant upgrades to the home, preparing for new ownership. A stunning Allen Park residence that seamlessly blends spacious living with contemporary amenities. Step into the open floor plan, featuring a main-level primary suite with ample closet space and a luxurious en-suite bathroom—a perfect retreat. The kitchen steals the spotlight with high-end appliances and stylish finishes, making it the heart of the home. Upstairs, three bedrooms, each equipped with generous closet space. The basement offers versatile space for a home office, gym, or entertainment area. Dual furnace heating ensures year-round comfort. Located in the sought-after Allen Park School District, this home perfectly marries convenience and practicality. Don't miss the chance to call this beautiful house your forever home. Certificate of occupancy provided at closing.
